(holdsIn WorldWarII (allies Germany Italy)) ; Japan?
(opponentsInConflict UnitedStatesOfAmerica Germany WorldWarII)
(opponentsInConflict UnitedStatesOfAmerica Italy WorldWarII)
(opponentsInConflict UnitedStatesOfAmerica Japan WorldWarII)
(opponentsInConflict Russia Germany WorldWarII)
